with info    good 20130807
with info    last 20080811
with version stable 1.8-src
with role    video
with trait   console
with source  stable $SOURCEFORGE_URL heroines/releases/081108/libmpeg3-$VERSION.tar.bz2
with info    home http://heroinewarrior.com/libmpeg3.php3
with info    cite 'library for editing mpeg streams
libmpeg3 decodes MP2, MP3, AC3, MPEG-1 video,
MPEG-2 video, and DVD footage in a single library.
It supports many esoteric features like parallel video decoding,
frame-accurate editing, YUV 4:2:2, and ATSC transport stream decoding.'

build(){
make &&
make install DESTDIR="$DESTDIR"
}
